'''札波羅結核電廠'''（{{lang-uk|Запорізька АЕС}}）是[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]][[核电站|核电站]]，也是歐洲最大的核電廠。

它座落在[[扎波羅熱州|扎波羅熱州]][[扎波羅熱|扎波羅熱]]附近[[第聶伯河|第聶伯河]][[卡霍夫卡水庫|卡霍夫卡水庫]]河畔，靠近[[埃涅爾戈達爾|埃涅爾戈達爾]]。它建有六座[[水-水高能反应堆|VVER]]-1000[[壓水反應爐|壓水反應爐]]，各可輸出950[[瓦特#吉瓦（百萬瓩）|-{zh-hans:兆瓦; zh-hant:百萬瓦特}-]]的電力，總功率輸出為5,700-{zh-hans:兆瓦; zh-hant:百萬瓦特}-<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.industcards.com/nuclear-lt-ua.htm |title=Nuclear Power Plants in Lithuania & Ukraine |work=industcards.com |date=2010-01-31 |accessdate=2011-04-02 |archive-date=2012-12-09 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20121209092440/http://www.industcards.com/nuclear-lt-ua.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。前五座发电机组及核反应堆在1985年至1989年間陸續竣工營運，1995年再加建第六座。札波羅結核電廠供應了烏克蘭一半以上的核能電力，約佔全國總電量的五分之一。

[[火力發電廠|火力發電廠]][[扎波罗热热电站|扎波罗热热电站]]也位於附近，相距約3公里。2022年3月4日，這兩座電廠在[[2022年俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭|俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭]]的[[扎波罗热战役|扎波罗热战役]]中被[[俄羅斯軍隊|俄羅斯軍隊]]控制<ref name = "2022captureReuters">{{Cite news |last=Polityuk |first=Pavel |last2=Vasovic |first2=Aleksandar |last3=Irish |first3=John |date=2022-03-04 |title=Russian forces seize huge Ukrainian nuclear plant, fire extinguished |language=en |work=Reuters |url=https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/top-wrap-1-europes-largest-nuclear-power-plant-fire-after-russian-attack-mayor-2022-03-04/ |access-date=2022-03-04 |archive-date=4 March 2022 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20220304100517/https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/top-wrap-1-europes-largest-nuclear-power-plant-fire-after-russian-attack-mayor-2022-03-04/ |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name = "2022captureBloomberg">{{Cite web |last=Daniel Ten Kate |first=David Stringer |date=2022-03-04 |title=Russian Forces Occupy Site of Nuclear Plant as Fire Contained |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-03-04/russia-firing-on-zaporizhzhia-nuclear-plant-ukraine-says?utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=socialflow-organic&utm_source=facebook&utm_content=business&cmpid=socialflow-facebook-business&fbclid=IwAR2yZVX2jcqhsBEmaat7Cn53PGWRcI4HHBd2PJDYaWWrUDjvqqPktues9sQ |url-status=live |archive-url= https://archive.today/20220304120723/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-03-04/russia-firing-on-zaporizhzhia-nuclear-plant-ukraine-says?utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=socialflow-organic&utm_source=facebook&utm_content=business&cmpid=socialflow-facebook-business&fbclid=IwAR2yZVX2jcqhsBEmaat7Cn53PGWRcI4HHBd2PJDYaWWrUDjvqqPktues9sQ |archive-date=4 March 2022 |access-date=2022-03-04 |website=Bloomberg }}</ref><ref name=2022captureCA /><ref name="2022captureNDTV1" />。據報導，該工廠現在由俄羅斯公司[[俄羅斯國家原子能公司|俄羅斯國家原子能公司(Rosatom)]]控制<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |title=Invaders seize Zaporizhzhia power plant and claims it is part of Rosatom |url=https://www.pravda.com.ua/eng/news/2022/03/12/7330624/ |access-date=20