== 運行狀態 ==
2017年，3號機組完成了現代化改造工作，將使用壽命延長10年至2027年。 2021年，5號機組完成了現代化改造工作，延長了10年的使用壽命<ref name=wnn-20171107>{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/RS-Zaporozhe-3-enters-next-10-years-of-operation-07111701.html |title=Zaporozhe 3 enters next 10 years of operation |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=7 November 2017 |access-date=8 November 2017 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107183055/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/RS-Zaporozhe-3-enters-next-10-years-of-operation-07111701.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 2014年動亂 ==
{{main|頓巴斯戰爭}}

2014年5月，據稱40名自稱是“[[右区|右區黨]]”（{{lang-en|Right Sector}}, {{lang-uk|Правий сектор}}）代表的武裝成員試圖進入發電廠區域<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ukrinform.ua/ukr/news/ohorona_zaes_zablokuvala_grupu_ozbroe_nih_osib_1939062|title=Новини Укрінформ|website=www.ukrinform.ua|access-date=2022-03-03|archive-date=2014-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140721080643/http://www.ukrinform.ua/ukr/news/ohorona_zaes_zablokuvala_grupu_ozbroe_nih_osib_1939062|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 這些人在進入[[埃涅爾戈達爾|埃涅爾戈達爾]]之前被烏克蘭警察攔住。

扎波羅熱發電廠位於距離[[頓巴斯戰爭|頓巴斯戰區]]約200公里的戰區，那裡的戰斗在2014年變得非常激烈。2014年8月31日，[[綠色和平組織|綠色和平組織]]成員Tobias Münchmeyer 表示擔心該工廠可能會被來自戰區的重型火砲擊中。

== 事故 ==
=== 2014年事件 ===
2014年12月3日，[[總理|總理]][[阿爾謝尼·亞采尼克|亞采尼克]]宣布幾天前在扎波羅熱核電站發生了一起事故<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/03/ukraine-nuclear-plant-accident_n_6260390.html|publisher=Huffington Post|title=Ukraine Reports Accident At Nuclear Power Plant, But Says Poses No Danger|date=3 December 2014|accessdate=2022-03-03|archive-date=2014-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141203184539/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/03/ukraine-nuclear-plant-accident_n_6260390.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據報導，事故原因是電源插座系統[[短路|短路]]，與現場生產無關<ref>{{cite news | url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-ukraine-crisis-power-idUKKCN0JH0ZZ20141203 | work=Reuters | title=Ukraine energy minister says 'no threat' from accident at nuclear plant | date=3 December 2014 | accessdate=2022-03-03 | archive-date=2016-06-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630000455/http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-ukraine-crisis-power-idUKKCN0JH0ZZ20141203 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。 該工廠的6個反應堆之一於2014年12月兩次關閉。 這種情況以及烏克蘭燃煤發電站的煤炭短缺導致2014年12月初至12月下旬在全國范圍內輪流停電<ref name=engycrisUD14>[https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/ukraine-turns-off-reactor-at-nuclear-plant-after-accident-9947540.html Ukraine turns off reactor at its most powerful nuclear plant after 'accident'] {{Wayback|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/ukraine-turns-off-reactor-at-nuclear-plant-after-accident-9947540.html |date=20171019042339 }}, [[The_Independent|The Independent]] (28 December 2014)<br>[https://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/25/world/europe/ukraine-briefly-cuts-power-to-crimea-amid-dispute-with-russia-over-nato.html?_r=0 Ukraine Briefly Cuts Power to Crimea Amid Feud With Russia Over NATO] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/25/world/europe/ukraine-briefly-cuts-power-to-crimea-amid-dispute-with-russia-over-nato.html?_r=0 |date=20160729102937 }}, [[New_York_Times|New York Times]] (DEC. 24, 2014)<br>[http://itar-tass.com/en/economy/770172 Coal import to help avoid rolling blackouts in Ukraine — energy minister] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108051631/http://itar-tass.com/en/economy/770172 |date=January 8, 2015 }}, [[ITAR-TASS|ITAR-TASS]] (December 31, 2014)<br>[http://mashable.com/2014/12/03/ukraine-nuclear-plant-accident/ Rolling blackouts in Ukraine after nuclear plant accident] {{Wayback|url=http://mashable.com/2014/12/03/ukraine-nuclear-plant-accident/ |date=20201031172322 }}, br>[[Mashable|Mashable]] (Dec 03, 2014)<br>[https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-12-31/ukraine-to-import-coal-from-far-away-as-war-curtails-mines.html Ukraine to Import Coal From ‘Far Away’ as War Curtails Mines] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-12-31/ukraine-to-import-coal-from-far-away-as-war-curtails-mines.html |date=20150109121036 }}, [[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg News]] (Dec 31, 2014)</ref>。 

=== 2022年俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭 ===
{{See also|扎波罗热战役|埃涅尔戈达尔围城战}}

[[2022年俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭|2022年俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭]]時，當地居民以肉身護廠，阻止俄軍攻佔該廠。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20220303/OP6GZKXP65DB7CMQ3OLZC2AISY/|title=烏克蘭鄉民「肉身護核電廠」震撼影片曝光 整條馬路都是人！阻俄軍攻佔|date=2022年3月3日|website=蘋果日報|access-date=2022年3月3日|archive-date=2022年3月4日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304065430/https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20220303/OP6GZKXP65DB7CMQ3OLZC2AISY/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1號至4號機組於2022年2月25日繼續運行，而5號和6號機組已關閉<ref>{{cite web |last1=Belgium |first1=Central Office, NucNet a s b l , Brussels |date=25 February 2022 |title=Ukraine / Energoatom Shuts Down Zaporozhye-5 And -6 As Rest Of Fleet Remains Safe And Operational :: NucNet {{!}} The Independent Nuclear News Agency |url=https://www.nucnet.org/news/energoatom-shuts-down-zaporozhye-5-and-6-as-rest-of-fleet-remains-safe-and-operational-2-5-2022 |website=The Independent Global Nuclear News Agency |access-date=2022-03-03 |archive-date=2022-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220225203312/https://www.nucnet.org/news/energoatom-shuts-down-zaporozhye-5-and-6-as-rest-of-fleet-remains-safe-and-operational-2-5-2022 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2022年2月28日，[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]聲稱已經佔領了該工廠以及[[埃涅爾戈達爾|埃涅爾戈達爾]]市。 [[埃涅爾戈達爾|埃涅爾戈達爾]]市長德米特里·奧爾洛夫後來否認了這一說法<ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-02-28 |title=Енергодар і Запорізька АЕС під контролем ЗСУ: мер міста просить не вірити фейкам |url=https://fakty.com.ua/ua/ukraine/20220228-energodar-i-zaporizka-aes-pid-kontrolem-zsu-mer-mista-prosyt-ne-viryty-fejkam/ |access-date=2022-03-02 |website=ФАКТИ ICTV |language=uk |archive-date=2022-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220228171301/https://fakty.com.ua/ua/ukraine/20220228-energodar-i-zaporizka-aes-pid-kontrolem-zsu-mer-mista-prosyt-ne-viryty-fejkam/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

當地時間2022年3月3日深夜，俄軍開始向札波羅結核電廠外圍發動砲擊，至3月4日凌晨1時許，[[埃涅爾戈達爾|埃涅爾戈達爾]]市長Dmytro Orlov報告扎波罗热核电厂被俄军攻击后失火的消息<ref>{{cite news |title=Дмитро Орлов |url=https://t.me/orlovdmytroEn/169 |newspaper=Dmytro Orlov市長官方telegram |date=4 March 2022 |accessdate=2022-03-04 |archive-date=2022-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220510081918/https://t.me/orlovdmytroEn/169 }}，В результаті бесперервного обстрілу ворогом будівель та блоків найбільшої АЕС в Європі палає Запорізька Атомна станція!</ref>，凌晨兩點半起火燃燒，清晨6點20分火勢被撲滅<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://edition.cnn.com/europe/live-news/ukraine-russia-putin-news-03-04-22/h_78c4ffa8b38d6e36f0490a9560d86b1a|title=A fire at Ukraine's largest nuclear power plant has been put out.|date=2022年3月4日|website=CNN|access-date=2022年3月4日|archive-date=2022年3月6日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220306233708/https://edition.cnn.com/europe/live-news/ukraine-russia-putin-news-03-04-22/h_78c4ffa8b38d6e36f0490a9560d86b1a}}</ref>；烏克蘭內政部公佈在4日清晨公佈，訓練中心的一棟建築物一座五層樓的3、4、5樓被焚毁，無人受傷<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/mvs.gov.ua/posts/323447979810858|title=Оперативна інформація щодо атаки російських загарбників на Запорізьку АЕС станом на 4:00|date=2022年3月4日|website=烏克蘭內政部facebook}}</ref>。

烏克蘭總統澤連斯基譴責俄軍行為，並與美國總統拜登通電話。<ref>{{cite news |title=乌克兰最大核电厂遭攻失火 泽连斯基谴责俄：核恐怖 |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/烏克蘭最大核電廠遭攻失火-澤連斯基譴責俄核恐怖/a-61007367 |accessdate=2022-03-04 |archive-date=2022-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304065434/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%B8%E9%9B%BB%E5%BB%A0%E9%81%AD%E6%94%BB%E5%A4%B1%E7%81%AB-%E6%BE%A4%E9%80%A3%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E4%BF%84%E6%A0%B8%E6%81%90%E6%80%96/a-61007367 |dead-url=no }}</ref>經過激烈的戰鬥後，當天早上俄羅斯軍隊在確認輻射水平沒有變化後佔領了該發電廠<ref>{{cite news |last=Boynton |first=Sean |title=Russian troops capture Europe's largest power plant in Ukraine after intense battle |url=https://globalnews.ca/news/8658032/ukraine-russia-nuclear-plant-fire/ |newspaper=[[Global_News|Global News]] |date=4 March 2022 |accessdate=2022-03-04 |archive-date=2022-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305120527/https://globalnews.ca/news/8658032/ukraine-russia-nuclear-plant-fire/ }}</ref><ref name=2022captureCA>{{cite news |last=Boynton |first=Sean |title=Russian troops capture Europe's largest power plant in Ukraine after intense battle |url=https://globalnews.ca/news/8658032/ukraine-russia-nuclear-plant-fire/ |newspaper=[[Global_News|Global News]] |date=4 March 2022 |archive-date=4 March 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304062939/https://globalnews.ca/news/8658032/ukraine-russia-nuclear-plant-fire/ |url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="2022captureNDTV1">{{Cite web |title=Russia Seizes Ukraine Nuclear Plant Hours After Attack: 10 Points |url=https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/russia-ukraine-war-vladimir-putin-biden-latest-developments-updates-on-kyiv-kharkiv-russian-invasion-2802607 |access-date=2022-03-04 |website=NDTV.com |archive-date=4 March 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304130432/https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/russia-ukraine-war-vladimir-putin-biden-latest-developments-updates-on-kyiv-kharkiv-russian-invasion-2802607 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

而後，該核電廠所屬管理公司與[[国际原子能机构|国际原子能机构]]（IAEA）亦分別證實核電廠已被俄軍控制<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.energoatom.com.ua/ua/press_centr-19/novini_kompanii-20/p/kerivnik_ea_petro_kotin_naslidki-48962|title=Company news|date=2022年3月4日|website=Energoatom|access-date=2022年3月4日|archive-date=2022年3月5日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305131608/https://www.energoatom.com.ua/ua/press_centr-19/novini_kompanii-20/p/kerivnik_ea_petro_kotin_naslidki-48962}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.iaea.org/zh/newscenter/pressreleases/zui-xin-qing-kuang-11-guo-ji-yuan-zi-neng-ji-gou-zong-gan-shi-guan-yu-wu-ke-lan-ju-shi-de-sheng-ming|title=最新情况11 — 国际原子能机构总干事关于乌克兰局势的声明|date=2022年3月4日|website=[[国际原子能机构|国际原子能机构]]|access-date=2022年3月5日|archive-date=2022年6月8日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220608054228/https://www.iaea.org/zh/newscenter/pressreleases/zui-xin-qing-kuang-11-guo-ji-yuan-zi-neng-ji-gou-zong-gan-shi-guan-yu-wu-ke-lan-ju-shi-de-sheng-ming}}</ref>及後核電廠管理方透過[[烏克蘭能源部|烏克蘭能源部]]向IAEA報告稱：被俄軍控制後核電廠如常運作，第2與第4反應堆如常運作；而烏克蘭境內另外三個核電廠亦如常運作<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.iaea.org/zh/newscenter/pressreleases/zui-xin-qing-kuang-12-guo-ji-yuan-zi-neng-ji-gou-zong-gan-shi-guan-yu-wu-ke-lan-ju-shi-de-sheng-ming|title=最新情况12 — 国际原子能机构总干事关于乌克兰局势的声明|date=2022年3月5日|website=[[国际原子能机构|国际原子能机构]]|access-date=2022年3月5日|archive-date=2022年6月6日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220606061509/https://www.iaea.org/zh/newscenter/pressreleases/zui-xin-qing-kuang-12-guo-ji-yuan-zi-neng-ji-gou-zong-gan-shi-guan-yu-wu-ke-lan-ju-shi-de-sheng-ming}}</ref>。

截至世界標準時間3月4日凌晨4點20分，國際原子能機構表示，位於訓練大樓的大火已被撲滅。 它不會影響反應堆安全或任何基本設備<ref>{{Cite web |title=IAEA appeal after shelling and fire at Zaporozhe : Regulation & Safety - World Nuclear News |url=https://www.world-nuclear-news.org/Articles/IAEA-appeal-after-shelling-and-fire-at-Zaporozhe |access-date=2022-03-04 |website=www.world-nuclear-news.org |archive-date=2022-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324104310/https://www.world-nuclear-news.org/Articles/IAEA-appeal-after-shelling-and-fire-at-Zaporozhe }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-03-04 |title=IAEA Director General Grossi's Initiative to Travel to Ukraine |url=https://www.iaea.org/newscenter/pressreleases/iaea-director-general-grossis-initiative-to-travel-to-ukraine |access-date=2022-03-04 |website=www.iaea.org |language=en |archive-date=2022-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220627103709/https://www.iaea.org/newscenter/pressreleases/iaea-director-general-grossis-initiative-to-travel-to-ukraine }}</ref>。該工廠損失了 1.3 GW (吉瓦)的容量，隨後附近的[[扎波罗热热电站|火力發電站]]增加了9台發電機組發電來補償<ref>{{cite web|date=2022-03-04|title=TPP compensates for the shutdown of Zaporizhzhya NPP|url=https://energo.dtek.com/en/media-center/press/dtek-tpps-compensates-for-the-shutdown-of-units-of-zaporizhzhya-npp-due-to-attack-by-occupiers-/|website=www.dtek.com|access-date=4 March 2022|archive-date=2022-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305115434/https://energo.dtek.com/en/media-center/press/dtek-tpps-compensates-for-the-shutdown-of-units-of-zaporizhzhya-npp-due-to-attack-by-occupiers-/}}</ref>。這是歷史上第二次有核電廠在軍事行動中被敵方佔領。當砲擊或各種攻擊造成該核電廠內的電力中斷，反應爐冷卻過程也就會中斷，如果[[核燃料|核燃料]]的溫度超過其熔點、放射性物質突破[[安全殼|安全殼]]，結果就是[[爐心熔毀|爐心熔毀]]導致[[輻射外洩|輻射外洩]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=砲擊核電廠有多危險？不必直接損毀反應爐　中斷電力最糟可能像福島核災|url=https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20220305/6CTOCOJ6HND7ZPMUGI7IS2AUF4/|access-date=2022-03-20|archive-date=2022-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304192718/https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20220305/6CTOCOJ6HND7ZPMUGI7IS2AUF4/}}</ref>

